  "content": "ed: Compiles and tests pass\n\n- [ ] **Step 6: Commit**\n\n```bash\ncd /workspaces/corvia-workspace/repos/corvia\ngit add crates/corvia-server/src/mcp.rs\ngit commit -m \"feat(server): add content_role/source_origin filters to MCP search and write tools\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 1.7: Run full workspace test suite\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: Run all tests**\n\nRun: `cd /workspaces/corvia-workspace/repos/corvia && cargo test --workspace`\nExpected: All 433+ tests pass. No regressions from metadata changes.\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: Verify existing `.corvia/knowledge/` entries still load**\n\nThe `#[serde(default)]` on the new fields means all existing JSON entries deserialize without changes. Verify by running `corvia search \"test\"` if the server is running, or by running the LiteStore deserialization tests.\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: Commit any fixups if needed, then push**\n\n```bash\ncd /workspaces/corvia-workspace/repos/corvia && git push\n```\n\n---\n",
